This is a perfectly viable option. I won't decry hard research to properly block in your execution of hard sci-fi with some grounding in extant scientific theory. You take this time to commit yourself to expanding your grasp of these concepts, so as to ensure technological consistency streamlining across the board, no matter how long you plan your story to be.
